Description:
@PAYBACK we are obsessed about data! Our platforms, products and services are as data driven as it gets and we never get tired of taking it to the next level. That’s why we’re looking for you, so you can guide and inspire our Software Engineering Teams in the DATA department (Munich and Warsaw).
We give you the flexibility and top management backing you need to really have an impact on how to build data-intensive applications on the intersection of Data + Software Engineering. Buzzwords and inflated egos are not our thing. We are looking for a humble thought leader, a visionary architect, someone who really cares about software engineering principles applied to massive amounts of data, an agile player and a people leader who never stopped coding.
YOUR TASKS
